{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"This is the exact moment"},{"time":4000,"text":"that I started creating something called Tinkering School."}]},{"cues":[{"time":9000,"text":"Tinkering School is a place where kids can pick up sticks"},{"time":13000,"text":"and hammers and other dangerous objects,"},{"time":17000,"text":"and be trusted."},{"time":19000,"text":"Trusted not to hurt themselves,"},{"time":21000,"text":"and trusted not to hurt others."},{"time":25000,"text":"Tinkering School doesn't follow a set curriculum,"},{"time":28000,"text":"and there are no tests."},{"time":30000,"text":"We're not trying to teach anybody any specific thing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":34000,"text":"When the kids arrive"},{"time":37000,"text":"they're confronted with lots of stuff:"},{"time":39000,"text":"wood and nails and rope and wheels,"},{"time":43000,"text":"and lots of tools, real tools."},{"time":48000,"text":"It's a six-day immersive experience for the kids."},{"time":53000,"text":"And within that context, we can offer the kids time --"},{"time":57000,"text":"something that seems in short supply"},{"time":60000,"text":"in their over-scheduled lives."},{"time":63000,"text":"Our goal is to ensure that they leave"},{"time":66000,"text":"with a better sense of how to make things"},{"time":68000,"text":"than when they arrived,"},{"time":71000,"text":"and the deep internal realization"},{"time":74000,"text":"that you can figure things out by fooling around."}]},{"cues":[{"time":78000,"text":"Nothing ever turns out as planned ... ever."},{"time":83000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":85000,"text":"And the kids soon learn"},{"time":87000,"text":"that all projects go awry --"},{"time":91000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":92000,"text":"and become at ease with the idea that every step"},{"time":94000,"text":"in a project is a step closer"},{"time":97000,"text":"to sweet success,"},{"time":100000,"text":"or gleeful calamity."},{"time":104000,"text":"We start from doodles and sketches."},{"time":108000,"text":"And sometimes we make real plans."},{"time":111000,"text":"And sometimes we just start building."},{"time":115000,"text":"Building is at the heart of the experience:"},{"time":118000,"text":"hands on, deeply immersed"},{"time":121000,"text":"and fully committed to the problem at hand."},{"time":125000,"text":"Robin and I, acting as collaborators,"},{"time":128000,"text":"keep the landscape of the projects"},{"time":130000,"text":"tilted towards completion."},{"time":133000,"text":"Success is in the doing,"},{"time":136000,"text":"and failures are celebrated and analyzed."},{"time":139000,"text":"Problems become puzzles"},{"time":142000,"text":"and obstacles disappear."}]},{"cues":[{"time":146000,"text":"When faced with particularly difficult"},{"time":148000,"text":"setbacks or complexities,"},{"time":150000,"text":"a really interesting behavior emerges: decoration."},{"time":155000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":158000,"text":"Decoration of the unfinished project"},{"time":160000,"text":"is a kind of conceptual incubation."},{"time":164000,"text":"From these interludes come deep insights"},{"time":167000,"text":"and amazing new approaches to solving the problems"},{"time":170000,"text":"that had them frustrated just moments before."}]},{"cues":[{"time":175000,"text":"All materials are available for use."},{"time":180000,"text":"Even those mundane, hateful, plastic grocery bags"},{"time":186000,"text":"can become a bridge"},{"time":188000,"text":"stronger than anyone imagined."},{"time":192000,"text":"And the things that they build"},{"time":195000,"text":"amaze even themselves."}]},{"cues":[{"time":198000,"text":"Video: Three, two, one, go!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":209000,"text":"Gever Tulley: A rollercoaster built by seven-year-olds."}]},{"cues":[{"time":213000,"text":"Video: Yay!"},{"time":216000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":218000,"text":"GT: Thank you. It's been a great pleasure."},{"time":221000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}